WEBVTT

00:00.271 --> 00:03.003
Daniel: WHAT IS YOUR DEEPEST,
DARKEST SECRET?

00:03.003 --> 00:05.406
THE ONE
YOU'VE NEVER TOLD A SOUL.

00:05.406 --> 00:07.338
I DON'T KNOW. DID --

00:07.338 --> 00:09.340
DID YOU BETRAY
A FRIEND'S CONFIDENCE

00:09.340 --> 00:12.243
OR SHOPLIFT
FROM THE CAMPUS STORE?

00:12.243 --> 00:15.116
MAYBE YOU'RE DYING
TO SLEEP WITH THE GIRL

00:15.116 --> 00:16.517
SITTING IN FRONT OF YOU?

00:16.517 --> 00:18.619
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:18.619 --> 00:20.691
OH, SORRY. I JUST --
LUCKY GUESS.

00:23.023 --> 00:24.495
HOW ABOUT YOU?
YOU GOT A SECRET?

00:26.297 --> 00:28.629
LEWICKI? YOU GOT -- NEVER MIND.
I-I DON'T WANT TO KNOW.

00:28.629 --> 00:30.161
[ LAUGHTER ]
RIGHT NOW,

00:30.161 --> 00:32.433
THERE IS A WAR
GOING ON IN YOUR BRAIN.

00:32.433 --> 00:35.306
OUR BEST GUESS
IS THAT YOUR CINGULATE CORTEX

00:35.306 --> 00:37.608
DESPERATELY
WANTS TO TELL THE TRUTH.

00:37.608 --> 00:40.040
BUT YOUR ORBITAL
PREFRONTAL CORTEX

00:40.040 --> 00:42.373
IS SIMULATING
HOW BAD THINGS WILL BE

00:42.373 --> 00:44.245
IF YOU ACTUALLY
SPILL THE BEANS.

00:44.245 --> 00:46.046
IF YOUR PREFRONTAL CORTEX WINS,

00:46.046 --> 00:47.818
YOUR LEVEL OF STRESS HORMONES
GOES UP.

00:47.818 --> 00:51.322
IF THE CINGULATE CORTEX WINS,
YOUR STRESS LEVEL DROPS.

00:51.322 --> 00:55.186
SO, IF IT'S
BIOLOGICALLY HEALTHIER

00:55.186 --> 00:58.459
TO CONFESS OUR SECRETS,
WHAT IS IT ABOUT HUMAN NATURE

00:58.459 --> 01:02.333
THAT MAKES US FIGHT SO HARD
TO KEEP THEM HIDDEN?

01:06.397 --> 01:09.600
DOUBLE SHOT AMERICANO.

01:11.442 --> 01:13.744
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

01:13.744 --> 01:15.206
WHAT?

01:15.206 --> 01:16.607
IT'S JUST
AN INCREDIBLY OVERPRICED,

01:16.607 --> 01:18.249
OVER-PROCESSED
CUP OF COFFEE.

01:20.411 --> 01:23.414
I GOT ASSIGNED
THE CARL HUFFMAN CASE.

01:23.414 --> 01:24.685
AHH.

01:24.685 --> 01:26.617
THE REAL-ESTATE MOGUL
WHO GOT BUSTED

01:26.617 --> 01:29.360
FOR RUNNING PONZI SCHEMES
OUT OF RETIREMENT CENTERS.

01:29.360 --> 01:31.492
YEAH,
NOT EXACTLY BERNIE MADOFF.

01:31.492 --> 01:34.365
BUT HE DID DUPE
A LOT OF OLD LADIES

01:34.365 --> 01:36.197
OUT OF THEIR PENSIONS.

01:36.197 --> 01:38.569
I NEED SOMEONE TO DO BACKGROUND
INTERVIEWS WITH THE VICS.

01:38.569 --> 01:40.301
YOU KNOW...
[ SIGHS ]

01:40.301 --> 01:42.773
...I'M JUST A LITTLE BIT BUSY
TO DO RETIREMENT-HOME VISITS.

01:42.773 --> 01:44.435
BUT THE OLD BIDDIES
LOVE YOU.

01:46.106 --> 01:47.778
YOU KNOW,
DANIEL ONCE WROTE

01:47.778 --> 01:50.241
A FASCINATING ARTICLE
ON THE NEUROSCIENCE OF CON MEN.

01:50.241 --> 01:51.782
MAYBE HE CAN HELP ME.

01:51.782 --> 01:53.614
WHY DO YOU ALWAYS FEEL THE NEED
TO INVOLVE THAT GUY?

01:53.614 --> 01:55.186
BECAUSE HE'S BRILLIANT.

01:55.186 --> 01:58.219
OH, AND UNLIKE ME,
HE NEVER SAYS NO TO A CASE.

01:58.219 --> 02:00.221
ABSOLUTELY NOT.
I DON'T HAVE TIME.

02:00.221 --> 02:02.753
YOU ALREADY AGREED
TO MEET HER.
I DID? WHY?

02:02.753 --> 02:04.755
SHE'S A PRETTY BIG
ENVIRONMENTAL ACTIVIST,

02:04.755 --> 02:06.457
AND SHE FLEW HERE
JUST FOR THIS.

02:06.457 --> 02:09.600
WELL, TELL HER I ALREADY GAVE
TO GREENPEACE THIS YEAR.

02:09.600 --> 02:12.463
I'M NOT HERE TO TALK ABOUT
SICK WHALES, DR. PIERCE.

02:14.134 --> 02:15.506
REBECCA ABBOT.

02:15.506 --> 02:17.808
I'M A HUGE FAN.
I'VE READ ALL YOUR BOOKS.

02:17.808 --> 02:20.541
WELL, I...

02:20.541 --> 02:22.513
SUPPOSE I COULD SPARE
A COUPLE OF MINUTES.

02:22.513 --> 02:23.774
GOOD.

02:23.774 --> 02:24.915
'CAUSE THERE'S SOMETHING
YOU NEED TO SEE.

02:26.547 --> 02:29.480
IT LOOKS LIKE TOURETTE'S.

02:29.480 --> 02:30.921
YEP.
NOW LOOK AT THIS.

02:30.921 --> 02:32.523
ALL OF THESE GIRLS
LIVE IN THE SAME SMALL TOWN,

02:32.523 --> 02:36.427
AND THEY ALL SPONTANEOUSLY
DEVELOPED SYMPTOMS

02:36.427 --> 02:37.658
WITHIN DAYS OF EACH OTHER.

02:37.658 --> 02:39.159
THAT DOESN'T MAKE SENSE.

02:39.159 --> 02:41.832
TOURETTE'S ISN'T
COMMUNICABLE.
EXACTLY.

02:41.832 --> 02:44.565
SO, WHAT'S
YOUR INVOLVEMENT?

02:44.565 --> 02:47.167
ONE OF THE GIRLS' MOTHERS
FOUND MY WEBSITE

02:47.167 --> 02:48.339
AND ASKED FOR MY HELP.

02:48.339 --> 02:49.770
SHE THINKS
THE GIRLS WERE POISONED.

02:49.770 --> 02:51.372
AN ENVIRONMENTAL
CONTAMINANT.

02:51.372 --> 02:53.374
T.C.E. --
TRICHLOROETHYLENE.

02:53.374 --> 02:55.246
THE CHEMICAL PLANT
IS THE BIGGEST EMPLOYER

02:55.246 --> 02:57.848
IN THE COUNTY,
PROCESSES TONS OF THIS STUFF.

02:57.848 --> 02:59.580
YOU'D HAVE TO PROVE
EXPOSURE.

02:59.580 --> 03:01.912
TOX SCREENS ON THE GIRLS
CAME BACK POSITIVE FOR T.C.E.

03:01.912 --> 03:04.315
WE'RE TESTING THE SOIL
AND GROUNDWATER NOW.

03:04.315 --> 03:06.587
10 TO ONE THIS STUFF IS LEECHING
INTO THE WATER SUPPLY.

03:06.587 --> 03:08.319
AND YOU THINK
THE COMPANY'S COVERING IT UP?

03:08.319 --> 03:10.461
[ SCOFFS ] I'M FILING
A CLASS ACTION LAWSUIT

03:10.461 --> 03:11.962
AGAINST BROOKSVILLE CHEMICAL.

03:11.962 --> 03:14.925
IF I COULD HAVE ONE OF
THE NATION'S TOP NEUROSCIENTISTS

03:14.925 --> 03:17.798
TESTIFY THAT T.C.E.
CAUSED THESE GIRLS' SYMPTOMS,

03:17.798 --> 03:19.370
IT MIGHT SEAL THE DEAL.

03:19.370 --> 03:21.472
WELL, I'D HAVE TO EXAMINE
THE GIRLS FIRST.

03:21.472 --> 03:23.334
COULD YOU DO IT
THIS WEEKEND?

03:23.334 --> 03:26.477
I'LL COVER YOUR PLANE TICKET
AND HOTEL.
PLANE TICKET?

03:26.477 --> 03:28.479
WH-- WHERE EXACTLY
IS THIS PLACE?

03:28.479 --> 03:30.541
BROOKSVILLE, PENNSYLVANIA.

03:30.541 --> 03:32.743
THIS REALLY ISN'T
A GOOD TIME.

03:32.743 --> 03:34.615
BUT, DR. PIERCE,
THESE GIRLS NEED YOUR HELP.

03:34.615 --> 03:37.488
THANKS FOR COMING IN,
MS. ABBOTT.

03:37.488 --> 03:39.219
THANKS...

03:39.219 --> 03:41.622
FOR WASTING MY TIME,
DR. PIERCE.

03:45.626 --> 03:47.498
SORRY!

03:47.498 --> 03:49.360
DIDN'T REALIZE
YOU WERE BUSY.

03:49.360 --> 03:51.902
NOTHING IMPORTANT.
GOOD.

03:51.902 --> 03:53.634
THEN YOU CAN HELP ME BRING DOWN
A MILLIONAIRE MOGUL

03:53.634 --> 03:56.437
WHO MADE HIS FORTUNE
BILKING NURSING-HOME RESIDENTS.

03:56.437 --> 03:58.969
ACTUALLY, I CAN'T.

03:58.969 --> 04:00.441
WHY NOT?

04:00.441 --> 04:03.243
I'M -- I'M ALREADY WORKING
ON A CASE.

04:03.243 --> 04:04.875
FOR THE FBI?

04:04.875 --> 04:08.449
NO. NO -- FOR, UH --
FOR REBECCA ABBOTT,

04:08.449 --> 04:11.922
THE...
HUFFY LADY
WHO'S NOT IMPORTANT?

04:11.922 --> 04:14.254
THE RENOWNED
ENVIRONMENTAL ACTIVIST.

04:14.254 --> 04:15.786
LEWICKI AND I
ARE GONNA BE OUT OF TOWN

04:15.786 --> 04:17.488
FOR A COUPLE OF DAYS,
RIGHT?

04:17.488 --> 04:19.530
MM-HMM?
RIGHT. RIGHT.

04:19.530 --> 04:22.933
SO, UM,
MAYBE NEXT TIME.

04:25.596 --> 04:26.597
[ DOOR OPENS ]

04:26.597 --> 04:28.839
[ SIGHS ]

04:30.501 --> 04:33.644
YOU'RE GONNA SIT
ON A PLANE FOR TWO HOURS

04:33.644 --> 04:37.047
AND THEN STAY IN A STRANGE,
MUSTY HOTEL ROOM IN A HICK TOWN

04:37.047 --> 04:38.479
BECAUSE YOU'RE
INTERESTED IN A CASE?

04:38.479 --> 04:39.550
HEY, THIS CASE --

04:39.550 --> 04:40.811
WHAT IS REALLY
GOING ON?

04:40.811 --> 04:44.284
[ SIGHS ] OKAY.

04:44.284 --> 04:48.689
KATE'S EX-HUSBAND TOLD ME
SHE HAS A THING FOR ME.

04:48.689 --> 04:50.791
I MEAN, HE'S AN IDIOT,
BUT I-I -- [ SIGHS ]

04:50.791 --> 04:52.723
I CAN'T HELP WONDERING
IF HER ASKING ME

04:52.723 --> 04:54.425
TO HELP ON CASES
ALL THE TIME

04:54.425 --> 04:56.296
IS JUST A WAY
TO GET CLOSER TO ME.

04:56.296 --> 04:59.800
WOULD THAT BE SO BAD?
KATE'S BRIGHT. SHE'S ATTRACTIVE.

04:59.800 --> 05:01.932
SHE ACCEPTS YOU
FOR WHO YOU ARE.
ARE YOU KIDDING ME?

05:01.932 --> 05:05.536
SHE'S INCREDIBLE,
BUT I-I CAN'T SUBJECT ANYONE

05:05.536 --> 05:07.678
TO THE CRAZINESS OF MY LIFE,
ESPECIALLY HER.

05:07.678 --> 05:10.080
SO YOUR SOLUTION
IS TO SCAMPER OUT OF TOWN

05:10.080 --> 05:11.742
EVERY TIME SHE COMES AROUND
WITH A CASE?

05:11.742 --> 05:13.313
I DON'T SCAMPER.

05:13.313 --> 05:15.315
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO BE HONEST
WITH HER EVENTUALLY.

05:15.315 --> 05:18.989
DOC? READY TO GO?

05:18.989 --> 05:21.852
ARE YOU REALLY
GONNA GO THROUGH WITH THIS?
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

05:21.852 --> 05:23.724
HOW BAD COULD IT BE?

05:23.724 --> 05:25.325
[ BABY CRYING ]

05:30.861 --> 05:33.364
[ BELL TONES ]

05:42.443 --> 05:43.774
[ RUMBLING ]

05:48.348 --> 05:50.120
[ CRUNCH ]

05:52.753 --> 05:53.884
[ THUD ]

05:53.884 --> 05:56.356
HERE YOU GO.
OHH!

05:56.356 --> 05:58.859
OH, I AM SO SORRY.

06:01.832 --> 06:04.565
OH, I CAN'T STAY HERE.

06:04.565 --> 06:05.836
WHY NOT?
NO. NO.
ARE YOU KIDDING ME?

06:05.836 --> 06:06.937
WITH THE -- THE --

06:06.937 --> 06:08.899
THE FAUX
THOMAS KINKADE ARTWORK

06:08.899 --> 06:11.642
AND THE -- THE ARTIFICIAL
BONSAI TOPIARIES,

06:11.642 --> 06:13.744
AND THE BACTERIA-INFESTED
BED COVERS. NO. NO.

06:13.744 --> 06:15.045
THIS IS NOT GONNA WORK.
DR. PIERCE?

06:15.045 --> 06:17.608
HI, I'M CHAD,
REBECCA'S ASSISTANT.

06:18.509 --> 06:20.511
OKAY, UH,
I'M SORRY I'M LATE,

06:20.511 --> 06:22.783
BUT SOMEONE SLASHED THE TIRES
ON OUR RENTAL CAR AGAIN.

06:22.783 --> 06:24.755
AGAIN?
YEAH, NOT EVERYBODY
IN REDNECKVILLE

06:24.755 --> 06:27.758
IS HAPPY THAT WE'RE HERE.
SORRY, WHAT ARE --
WHAT ARE WE LATE FOR?

06:27.758 --> 06:29.059
THE TOWN-HALL MEETING.

06:29.059 --> 06:30.791
I'M NOT HERE
FOR ANY TOWN-HALL MEETING.

06:30.791 --> 06:32.923
I'M HERE TO EXAMINE THE GIRLS.
THAT'S WHERE THEY ARE.

06:32.923 --> 06:36.527
DOC, JUST GO, OKAY?
I GOT THIS COVERED.

06:36.527 --> 06:38.929
[ SIGHS ]
GREAT. FANTASTIC.

06:38.929 --> 06:41.902
THE -- THE BEDSPREAD.
I GOT IT, DOC.

06:41.902 --> 06:44.535
AND THOSE LITTLE -- THOSE --
I GOT IT.

06:44.535 --> 06:46.737
AND THE ARTWORK GOES.

06:48.408 --> 06:50.110
ESPECIALLY THAT ONE.

06:53.814 --> 06:55.415
Rebecca: LOOK AT WHAT
BROOKSVILLE CHEMICAL HAS DONE

06:55.415 --> 06:58.418
TO YOUR TOWN'S CHILDREN,
AND THAT'S NOT ALL.

06:58.418 --> 07:00.621
COMPARED TO THE REST
OF WESTERN PENNSYLVANIA,

07:00.621 --> 07:03.894
BROOKSVILLE HAS HIGHER RATES
OF CANCER, MISCARRIAGE,

07:03.894 --> 07:05.025
AND INFERTILITY.

07:05.025 --> 07:06.757
[ CROWD MURMURS ]

07:06.757 --> 07:10.931
WHAT'S THE DIFFERENCE
BETWEEN THEIR TOWN AND YOURS?

07:10.931 --> 07:13.103
BROOKSVILLE CHEMICAL!

07:13.103 --> 07:15.836
MARTIN SULLIVAN
AND HIS EXECUTIVES DO NOT CARE

07:15.836 --> 07:17.708
HOW MANY PEOPLE THEY HURT
IN THIS TOWN.

07:17.708 --> 07:19.069
LIAR!

07:19.069 --> 07:20.941
HOW DARE YOU SAY SUCH THINGS
ABOUT MY HUSBAND!

07:20.941 --> 07:23.213
I WON'T LISTEN TO ANY MORE
OF THIS BULLSHIT!

07:23.213 --> 07:26.977
Martin:
PLEASE, EXCUSE MY FAMILY.

07:26.977 --> 07:30.180
THEY'RE UPSET.
I'M UPSET.

07:30.180 --> 07:32.452
MY GRANDFATHER WORKED THE LAND
UNDER THE PLANT.

07:32.452 --> 07:35.125
MY FATHER STARTED THE COMPANY
WITH 10 EMPLOYEES.

07:35.125 --> 07:38.589
Rebecca: BROOKSVILLE CHEMICAL
MAY HAVE BEEN FOUNDED HERE,

07:38.589 --> 07:41.231
BUT IT IS A MULTINATIONAL
CORPORATION NOW.

07:41.231 --> 07:43.564
ALL THEY CARE ABOUT
IS THEIR STOCK PRICE.

07:43.564 --> 07:46.667
NO. WE STAYED IN THIS TOWN
TO BUILD THE LOCAL ECONOMY.

07:46.667 --> 07:49.069
IT'S YOUR FRIVOLOUS LAWSUIT
THAT CAN TURN BROOKSVILLE

07:49.069 --> 07:51.672
INTO THE NEXT FLINT,
MICHIGAN.

07:51.672 --> 07:54.474
CORPORATE ACCOUNTABILITY
IS NOT FRIVOLOUS!

07:54.474 --> 07:56.476
IT IS DEADLY SERIOUS!

07:56.476 --> 07:58.108
WHICH IS WHY I'VE FLOWN IN
ONE OF AMERICA'S

07:58.108 --> 08:01.011
MOST RENOWNED NEUROSCIENTISTS
TO HELP US WITH OUR CASE.

08:01.011 --> 08:04.154
EVERYONE,
THIS IS DR. DANIEL PIERCE.

08:05.986 --> 08:08.158
[ Distant ] HE'S COME
ALL THE WAY FROM CHICAGO

08:08.158 --> 08:12.492
TO EXAMINE THESE GIRLS
AND TO TESTIFY ON OUR BEHALF

08:12.492 --> 08:14.264
BECAUSE HE BELIEVES
WHAT I BELIEVE --

08:14.264 --> 08:17.728
THAT YOUR CHILDREN
HAVE BEEN POISONED.

08:17.728 --> 08:20.531
[ CROWD MURMURING ]

08:24.134 --> 08:25.706
DR. PIERCE!

08:25.706 --> 08:27.137
COULD THESE CHEMICALS
HAVE KILLED MY DAUGHTER?

08:27.137 --> 08:28.709
I REALLY -- I CAN'T --

08:28.709 --> 08:30.210
PLEASE. PLEASE.
JUST TAKE A LOOK.

08:32.012 --> 08:34.785
HETEROCHROMIA IRIDUM.
WHAT'S THAT?

08:34.785 --> 08:38.048
HER EYES --
ONE'S BLUE, ONE'S HAZEL.

08:38.048 --> 08:39.890
DID SHE HAVE THE SAME SPASMS
AS THE OTHER GIRLS?

08:39.890 --> 08:41.892
NO. LOOK.

08:43.994 --> 08:45.656
THIS IS
AN AUTOPSY REPORT.

08:45.656 --> 08:47.197
I WAS AWAY IN PITTSBURGH
FOR THE WEEKEND.

08:47.197 --> 08:49.930
I CAME HOME AND I FOUND PATTI.
SHE, UM...

08:49.930 --> 08:52.062
SHE HUNG HERSELF
IN HER CLOSET.

08:52.062 --> 08:53.734
I NEVER SHOULD HAVE
LEFT HER ALONE.

08:53.734 --> 08:55.165
I'M SORRY.

08:55.165 --> 08:57.537
I MEAN, MAYBE THOSE CHEMICALS
MADE HER DEPRESSED.

08:57.537 --> 08:59.810
I-I DON'T THINK T.C.E. POISONING
WOULD HAVE AFFECTED HER MOOD.

08:59.810 --> 09:01.211
IT'S -- IT'S NOT THE ANSWER
YOU'RE LOOKING FOR.
BUT --

09:01.211 --> 09:03.213
I'M SORRY.

09:03.213 --> 09:05.816
DR. PIERCE?!

09:05.816 --> 09:08.879
DR. PIERCE...
[ SIGHS ]

09:08.879 --> 09:11.752
ARE YOU TRYING
TO MAKE ME LOOK BAD?
HEY, YOU AMBUSHED ME!

09:11.752 --> 09:13.183
YOU POINTED ME OUT
IN FRONT OF ALL THOSE PEOPLE!

09:13.183 --> 09:14.825
I THOUGHT
THAT'S WHY YOU WERE HERE,

09:14.825 --> 09:16.957
TO PROVE BROOKSVILLE CHEMICAL
COVERED UP A SPILL!

09:16.957 --> 09:19.129
I AM HERE TO DO A NEUROLOGICAL
EXAMINATION OF THOSE GIRLS.

09:19.129 --> 09:21.091
YOU'RE THE ONE WHIPPING
THIS TOWN INTO HYSTERICS

09:21.091 --> 09:23.634
WITHOUT ANY PROOF!
THAT'S NOT TRUE!
OUR TEST RESULTS CAME BACK.

09:23.634 --> 09:25.636
THE TOWN'S GROUNDWATER
IS CONTAMINATED.

09:25.636 --> 09:27.237
[ GUNSHOT ]

09:27.237 --> 09:29.840
[ SCREAMING ]

09:40.350 --> 09:42.112
Max: HOW'S REBECCA?

09:42.112 --> 09:44.655
SHE'S LUCKY. SHOT IN THE ARM.
SHE'S IN SURGERY NOW.

09:44.655 --> 09:46.787
SLASHED TIRES,
NOW A SHOOTING.

09:46.787 --> 09:49.019
SHE'S OBVIOUSLY
ONTO SOMETHING.

09:49.019 --> 09:51.662
I GOT TO SEE THOSE GIRLS
TONIGHT.
NO, NO. LET'S HEAD
BACK TO THE ROOM FIRST.

09:51.662 --> 09:55.025
NO, DON'T -- IT'S IMPORTANT!
DOC, TAKE A BREATH,
AND PUT ON A CLEAN SHIRT, OKAY?

09:55.025 --> 09:56.627
[ ELEVATOR BELL RINGS ]

09:56.627 --> 09:58.368
OKAY.

10:01.632 --> 10:02.903
CHECK IT OUT.

10:02.903 --> 10:06.176
"EXTREME HOME MAKEOVER,"
BROOKSVILLE EDITION.

10:06.176 --> 10:08.639
EXTREME WHAT?
NOTHING.

10:08.639 --> 10:10.911
WHAT DO YOU THINK,
DOC?

10:10.911 --> 10:14.184
TURN THE DESK AROUND.
I CAN'T FACE THE WALL.

10:14.184 --> 10:15.916
OKAY.

10:15.916 --> 10:17.187
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

10:17.187 --> 10:19.790
[ SIGHS ]

10:19.790 --> 10:21.792
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]
YEAH.

10:21.792 --> 10:23.223
HE'S RIGHT HERE.
HOLD ON.

10:23.223 --> 10:24.955
DOC, IT'S KATE.

10:24.955 --> 10:26.697
TELL HER I'M BUSY.

10:26.697 --> 10:28.228
I CALLED HER,
AND I TOLD HER WHAT HAPPENED.

10:28.228 --> 10:30.100
WHY DID YOU DO THAT?!

10:30.100 --> 10:32.663
'CAUSE YOU ALMOST GOT SHOT,
AND SHE'S THE FBI.

10:32.663 --> 10:33.934
[ SIGHS ]

10:33.934 --> 10:36.336
HI.

10:36.336 --> 10:37.808
KATE: I'll be on
the next flight out.

10:37.808 --> 10:39.069
YOU REALLY
DON'T HAVE TO.

10:39.069 --> 10:41.071
Daniel,
somebody shot at you!

10:41.071 --> 10:43.143
PLUS, LEWICKI SAYS THAT PLACE
IS A REAL BACKWATER.

10:43.143 --> 10:45.045
THE LOCAL P.D.
ISN'T GONNA BE THAT THOROUGH,

10:45.045 --> 10:46.677
ESPECIALLY
IF IT'S A COMPANY TOWN.

10:46.677 --> 10:48.348
Yeah, well, isn't there
an FBI field office

10:48.348 --> 10:49.720
THAT CAN HANDLE IT?

10:49.720 --> 10:50.781
Whoa, Pittsburgh?

10:50.781 --> 10:52.282
YEAH, I DON'T, UH --

10:52.282 --> 10:53.653
I DON'T THINK THEY'RE
GONNA WANT TO WORK WITH YOU.

10:53.653 --> 10:54.985
WHY NOT?
Let's face it, Daniel.

10:54.985 --> 10:56.256
YOU'RE NOT EXACTLY
CONVENTIONAL.

10:56.256 --> 10:58.328
I-I GOT TO GO.
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

10:58.328 --> 11:01.792
DANIEL.

11:01.792 --> 11:03.163
CALL GRANOLA GUY.

11:03.163 --> 11:05.265
TELL HIM THAT I WANT TO SEE
THE SYMPTOMATIC GIRLS.

11:05.265 --> 11:06.867
BUT CAN IT WAIT
TILL MORNING?

11:06.867 --> 11:09.269
THOSE CORPORATE BASTARDS
ARE NOT GONNA INTIMIDATE ME.

11:09.269 --> 11:11.271
[ Stammering ]
TWO WEEKS AGO I WOKE UP,

11:11.271 --> 11:13.003
AND I COULDN'T CONTROL
MY ARM.

11:13.003 --> 11:14.875
MY NECK STARTED
THE NEXT DAY.

11:14.875 --> 11:16.276
IT'S JUST GOTTEN WORSE
SINCE THEN.

11:16.276 --> 11:18.208
SO, YOU CAN'T CONTROL
THE MOVEMENTS?

11:18.208 --> 11:21.882
NO, IT'S LIKE...
AN ITCH I HAVE TO SCRATCH.

11:21.882 --> 11:24.154
IT NEVER STOPS.
MNH! MNH!

11:24.154 --> 11:26.016
ARE YOU ABLE TO SLEEP?

11:26.016 --> 11:27.357
NOT SINCE IT STARTED.

11:27.357 --> 11:29.890
EVERY TIME I DOZE OFF,
I START TWITCHING.

11:29.890 --> 11:31.291
LET'S TALK ABOUT
YOUR SOCIAL LIFE.

11:31.291 --> 11:34.294
ANYTHING PARTICULARLY STRESSFUL
THERE RECENTLY?

11:34.294 --> 11:36.426
HELLO?
I'M A HIGH-SCHOOL GIRL

11:36.426 --> 11:38.028
WITH FACIAL TICS
AND ARM TREMORS.

11:38.028 --> 11:40.100
YOU DON'T THINK THAT QUALIFIES
AS STRESSFUL?!

11:41.902 --> 11:43.774
C-CAN I GO NOW?

11:43.774 --> 11:46.777
I WANT TO MEET
WITH ALL THEIR DOCTORS.

11:46.777 --> 11:48.178
HAVE THE GIRLS' PARENTS
SIGNED CONSENTS?

11:48.178 --> 11:49.780
UH,
YES TO THE CONSENTS,

11:49.780 --> 11:51.782
AND THERE'S ONLY
ONE PEDIATRICIAN IN BROOKSVILLE.

11:51.782 --> 11:53.313
THAT'S DR. BILSON.
HE TREATS ALL THE GIRLS.

11:53.313 --> 11:55.045
SO, I CAN SET UP A MEETING,
UH, TOMORROW.

11:55.045 --> 11:57.047
NO. NOW.

11:57.047 --> 11:59.319
YOU THINK
IT'S T.C.E. POISONING?

11:59.319 --> 12:02.422
ALL THESE TOX SCREENS
CONFIRM LOW LEVELS OF EXPOSURE,

12:02.422 --> 12:05.195
BUT I'M NOT SEEING
ANY NEUROTOXIC SYMPTOMS --

12:05.195 --> 12:07.397
NO...NO NUMBNESS
IN THE EXTREMITIES,

12:07.397 --> 12:09.129
NAUSEA, OR DIZZINESS.

12:09.129 --> 12:10.730
ARE YOU SAYING
THEY'RE FAKING IT?

12:10.730 --> 12:14.004
NO.
I-I DON'T THINK SO.

12:14.004 --> 12:16.867
DID ANY OF THE GIRLS
HAVE ANY HEALTH ISSUES

12:16.867 --> 12:18.338
BEFORE THE SYMPTOMS?

12:18.338 --> 12:22.312
SOME FLU CASES, A STREP-THROAT
OUTBREAK A FEW MONTHS AGO.

12:22.312 --> 12:24.845
I KNOW A COUPLE OF THE GIRLS
CAUGHT IT.

12:24.845 --> 12:26.346
IT'S CALLED PANDAS.

12:26.346 --> 12:28.819
YOU MEAN, LIKE, CUTE LITTLE
BLACK-AND-WHITE CHINESE BEARS?

12:28.819 --> 12:31.822
IT'S A NEUROPSYCHIATRIC DISORDER
IN CHILDREN,

12:31.822 --> 12:34.754
AND IT CAN CAUSE MOTOR
AND VOCAL TICS AND TREMORS.

12:34.754 --> 12:36.957
IT'S CAUSED
BY T.C.E. EXPOSURE?

12:36.957 --> 12:38.859
NO. IT'S CAUSED BY
STREPTOCOCCAL INFECTIONS.

12:38.859 --> 12:40.430
NOW, I HAVE TO DO
A FEW MORE TESTS,

12:40.430 --> 12:42.833
BUT AT LEAST THREE OF THOSE
GIRLS WERE TREATED FOR STREP.

12:42.833 --> 12:44.294
YOU'RE TELLING ME
THAT THIS PANDAS

12:44.294 --> 12:46.837
COULD HAVE CAUSED THE TICKING
AND NOT T.C.E. POISONING?

12:46.837 --> 12:49.469
HEY. SORRY TO INTERRUPT.
CNN CALLED.

12:49.469 --> 12:51.942
THEY WANT TO SEE
IF YOU'LL DO A LIVE REMOTE,

12:51.942 --> 12:53.373
TALK ABOUT THE CASE.

12:53.373 --> 12:54.975
HELL YES.

12:54.975 --> 12:57.247
GREAT.
DR. PIERCE...

12:57.247 --> 12:59.509
I FLEW YOU OUT HERE
TO SUPPORT MY CASE,

12:59.509 --> 13:01.311
NOT UNDERMINE IT.

13:01.311 --> 13:03.113
I'M HERE TO FIND OUT
WHY THOSE GIRLS ARE SICK,

13:03.113 --> 13:07.517
NOT JUST RUBBER-STAMP WHATEVER
THEORY SUPPORTS YOUR CASE.

13:07.517 --> 13:09.519
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

13:09.519 --> 13:11.021
[ SIGHS ]

13:20.270 --> 13:22.132
[ CREAK ]

13:22.132 --> 13:23.403
WOMAN: Help me, please.

13:23.403 --> 13:26.476
LEWICKI? IS THAT YOU?

13:31.011 --> 13:34.414
WOMAN:
Help me. Please, help me.

13:34.414 --> 13:38.588
Help me.

13:54.534 --> 13:56.266
[ SIGHS ]

14:07.517 --> 14:08.518
PATTI.

14:13.523 --> 14:16.987
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

14:27.267 --> 14:28.999
WHAT ARE
YOU DOING HERE?

14:28.999 --> 14:30.370
I DON'T KNOW WHY,

14:30.370 --> 14:31.871
BUT I THOUGHT YOU'D BE
A LITTLE HAPPIER TO SEE ME.

14:31.871 --> 14:33.944
WELL, I'M STILL
A LITTLE GROGGY.

14:33.944 --> 14:37.047
WHAT TIME IS IT?
I DON'T KNOW.
A LITTLE AFTER 8:00.

14:37.047 --> 14:38.378
GET DRESSED.

14:38.378 --> 14:39.950
I STOPPED BY THE LOCAL P.D.
ON MY WAY HERE.

14:39.950 --> 14:41.952
THEY DO NOT HAVE ANY SUSPECTS
IN THE SHOOTING.

14:41.952 --> 14:43.613
BUT I GRILLED THEM
A LITTLE BIT,

14:43.613 --> 14:45.485
AND THEY ADMITTED
THEY DO KNOW WHO VANDALIZED

14:45.485 --> 14:47.157
REBECCA'S RENTAL CAR.

14:47.157 --> 14:48.618
WHO?

14:48.618 --> 14:50.360
I DIDN'T SHOOT
THAT CRAZY BITCH.

14:50.360 --> 14:52.092
BUT YOU SLASHED
HER TIRES.

14:52.092 --> 14:55.365
THAT WAS JUST A PRANK.
BRADEN APOLOGIZED TO THE POLICE.

14:55.365 --> 14:58.198
MR. SULLIVAN,
DO YOU OWN A .22-CALIBER RIFLE?

14:58.198 --> 15:00.600
IF YOU'RE GONNA SUSPECT
EVERY PERSON IN THIS TOWN

15:00.600 --> 15:03.203
WHO HAS A RIFLE IN THEIR DEN
OF ATTEMPTED MURDER,

15:03.203 --> 15:05.375
YOU'VE GOT YOUR WORK
CUT OUT FOR YOU.
WELL, NOT EVERY PERSON IN TOWN

15:05.375 --> 15:08.478
JUST SAW THEIR FATHER
PUBLICLY DISPARAGED.

15:08.478 --> 15:10.480
BRADEN WAS
AT THE TOWN HALL WITH US

15:10.480 --> 15:13.483
AT THE TIME OF THE SHOOTING.
NO, ACTUALLY,
BRADEN STORMED OUT

15:13.483 --> 15:16.386
A FEW MINUTES BEFORE REBECCA
GOT SHOT, AS I RECALL,

15:16.386 --> 15:17.948
PLENTY OF TIME
TO GRAB A GUN.

15:17.948 --> 15:20.090
WE'RE DONE HERE,
BUT BEFORE YOU GO,

15:20.090 --> 15:21.451
I THINK YOU SHOULD KNOW

15:21.451 --> 15:24.194
THE COMPANY COMMISSIONED
ITS OWN T.C.E. TESTS.

15:24.194 --> 15:27.497
THE RESULTS JUST CAME BACK.

15:27.497 --> 15:31.431
NO CONTAMINATION IN THE SOIL,
THE AIR, OR AROUND THE SCHOOL.

15:33.103 --> 15:36.236
SO, BROOKSVILLE CHEMICAL
FINANCES ITS OWN STUDY

15:36.236 --> 15:39.109
AND THEN GIVES ITSELF
A CLEAN BILL OF HEALTH.

15:39.109 --> 15:43.073
YEAH, THERE'S NO
CONFLICT OF INTEREST THERE.

15:43.073 --> 15:45.945
I KNOW. I KNOW.

15:45.945 --> 15:48.979
WHAT IF IT'S REBECCA'S TESTS
THAT ARE OFF?

15:48.979 --> 15:50.520
YOU THINK SHE FAKED THEM?

15:50.520 --> 15:53.523
I DON'T KNOW.
WAIT A SECOND.

15:53.523 --> 15:55.155
IS DANIEL PIERCE SAYING
THAT MAYBE

15:55.155 --> 15:57.687
THE BIG BAD CORPORATION
ISN'T THE ENEMY?

15:57.687 --> 15:59.389
Daniel:
I'M JUST SAYING --

15:59.389 --> 16:03.033
SHE'S GOT A LOT TO GAIN
FROM PROVING T.C.E. EXPOSURE,

16:03.033 --> 16:04.334
AND -- AND
I'M STARTING TO THINK

16:04.334 --> 16:06.436
THIS IS MORE ABOUT MONEY
AND PUBLICITY FOR HER

16:06.436 --> 16:08.438
THAN IT IS THOSE GIRLS.

16:08.438 --> 16:10.700
I'LL SUBPOENA THE LAB
THAT DID REBECCA'S TESTING,

16:10.700 --> 16:13.303
MAKE SURE WE'RE SEEING
THE ORIGINAL REPORTS.

16:13.303 --> 16:15.505
BUT UNTIL WE HAVE PROOF,
SHE'S STILL A VICTIM.

16:15.505 --> 16:16.576
MAYBE NOT.

16:17.607 --> 16:20.750
I MEAN, IF THE TEST RESULTS
WERE PHONY...

16:20.750 --> 16:22.712
MAYBE THE SHOOTING WAS,
TOO.

16:26.616 --> 16:28.618
OH, HEY, DR. PIERCE.

16:28.618 --> 16:31.661
IF YOU ARE LOOKING FOR REBECCA,
SHE'S STILL IN THE HOSPITAL.

16:31.661 --> 16:33.493
THIS IS AGENT MORETTI
OF THE FBI.

16:33.493 --> 16:35.295
WE'RE ACTUALLY HERE
TO SEE YOU.

16:35.295 --> 16:37.297
ME?

16:37.297 --> 16:39.029
A WEEK AGO,
YOU DROVE TO LEXINGTON

16:39.029 --> 16:41.571
AND PURCHASED A WINCHESTER
BOLT ACTION .22.

16:41.571 --> 16:43.473
REBECCA WANTED TO MAKE IT LOOK
LIKE SHE WAS BEING TARGETED,

16:43.473 --> 16:46.636
BUT HITTING HER WASN'T REALLY
PART OF THE PLAN, WAS IT?

16:46.636 --> 16:49.679
OKAY, FIRST OFF, THAT'S CRAZY.
I WOULD NEVER ACTUALLY --
BALLISTICS ARE GONNA MATCH,
CHAD.

16:49.679 --> 16:52.142
YOU'RE ON THE HOOK
FOR ATTEMPTED MURDER.

16:56.146 --> 16:59.689
OKAY, I-I NEVER
TRIED TO KILL ANYBODY.

16:59.689 --> 17:01.391
YOU SHOT INTO A CROWD.
YOU'RE GOING TO JAIL.

17:04.023 --> 17:07.557
UNLESS, OF COURSE,
YOU HELP US OUT.

17:07.557 --> 17:09.529
Rebecca: YOU THINK
THIS IS A PUBLICITY STUNT?

17:09.529 --> 17:11.061
I NEARLY DIED.

17:11.061 --> 17:12.762
YEAH, ONLY BECAUSE CHAD
ISN'T A BETTER MARKSMAN.

17:12.762 --> 17:14.364
HE WAS ONLY
SUPPOSED TO SHOOT OUT

17:14.364 --> 17:15.705
THE WINDOW OF YOUR CAR.

17:15.705 --> 17:17.237
IT'S A GREAT STORY.
IT'S A GREAT STORY.

17:17.237 --> 17:19.309
THE -- THE ENVIRONMENTAL
CRUSADER RISKS HER LIFE

17:19.309 --> 17:21.171
TO BRING DOWN
THE CORPORATE CRIMINALS.

17:21.171 --> 17:23.643
I LOVE THAT STORY, AND THAT'S
WHAT REALLY PISSES ME OFF!

17:23.643 --> 17:25.415
THERE ARE SO MANY
CORPORATE CRIMINALS

17:25.415 --> 17:27.277
THAT WE COULD HAVE
GONE AFTER.

17:27.277 --> 17:29.579
AND INSTEAD, YOU SUCKED ME INTO
YOUR PETTY LITTLE SHAKEDOWN.

17:29.579 --> 17:31.481
THIS ISN'T A SHAKEDOWN!

17:31.481 --> 17:33.453
THE TOX SCREENS SHOW T.C.E.
IN THOSE GIRLS' BLOOD!
LOW LEVELS.

17:33.453 --> 17:35.185
I COULD TEST 100 PEOPLE
IN THIS TOWN,

17:35.185 --> 17:38.188
99 OF THEM WOULD COME BACK
POSITIVE FOR T.C.E.

17:38.188 --> 17:39.459
BECAUSE OF EMISSIONS
FROM THAT DAMN PLANT.

17:39.459 --> 17:41.531
BUT IT'S NOT ENOUGH
TO MAKE ANYONE SICK.

17:41.531 --> 17:43.293
THE STUFF IS LEACHING
INTO THE GROUNDWATER.

17:43.293 --> 17:44.834
BULLSHIT!

17:44.834 --> 17:47.437
WE KNOW YOUR ORIGINAL
TEST RESULTS CAME BACK CLEAN.

17:47.437 --> 17:49.299
YOU LIED TO ME, REBECCA.

17:49.299 --> 17:51.371
YOU NEVER HAD A CASE
AGAINST BROOKSVILLE CHEMICAL.

17:51.371 --> 17:53.473
BUT YOU THOUGHT THAT YOU COULD
STILL SQUEEZE THEM

17:53.473 --> 17:55.605
BY COOKING UP YOUR OWN
FRAUDULENT TEST RESULTS,

17:55.605 --> 17:58.778
ONLY MARTIN SULLIVAN WOULDN'T
CAVE IN TO YOUR DEMANDS.

17:58.778 --> 18:00.610
I'M THE VICTIM HERE.

18:00.610 --> 18:04.354
CHAD SIGNED A SWORN AFFIDAVIT.
HE'S TESTIFYING AGAINST YOU.

18:04.354 --> 18:07.857
HOW COULD YOU BELIEVE A WORD
THAT HEMP-ADDLED SIMPLETON SAYS?

18:07.857 --> 18:10.860
NOT ONLY DO WE BELIEVE HIM,
SO DOES THE U.S. ATTORNEY.

18:10.860 --> 18:13.823
SO, CHAD'S GETTING IMMUNITY.
IT'S OVER.

18:13.823 --> 18:15.865
I WAS LOOKING OUT
FOR THOSE GIRLS.

18:15.865 --> 18:18.398
NOW THEY'LL GET NOTHING.

18:18.398 --> 18:19.669
IF YOU HADN'T INTERFERED,
THEY WOULD HAVE WALKED AWAY

18:19.669 --> 18:21.371
WITH CLOSE TO
$1 MILLION EACH.

18:21.371 --> 18:25.104
YEAH, AND YOU WOULD HAVE
GOTTEN 33%, SO...

18:26.836 --> 18:28.538
MA'AM,
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST.

18:28.538 --> 18:30.680
YOU HAVE THE RIGHT
TO REMAIN SILENT.

18:30.680 --> 18:32.111
ANYTHING YOU SAY...

18:32.111 --> 18:34.714
[ INDISTINCT TALKING
IN DISTANCE ]

18:40.520 --> 18:43.593
DANIEL!

18:49.759 --> 18:51.401
Help me.

18:51.401 --> 18:53.463
DR. PIERCE.

18:54.764 --> 18:57.667
I'VE BEEN LOOKING FOR YOU.
WHAT'S WRONG?

18:57.667 --> 18:59.409
THREE MORE OF MY PATIENTS
ARE SYMPTOMATIC,

18:59.409 --> 19:01.541
AND I'VE GOT CALLS
FROM TWO OTHER PARENTS.

19:01.541 --> 19:04.344
I MEAN, WHATEVER THIS THING IS,
IT'S SPREADING.

19:11.851 --> 19:14.153
SEVEN GIRLS SPONTANEOUSLY
DEVELOP UNCONTROLLABLE SPASMS.

19:14.153 --> 19:15.425
IT'S IMPOSSIBLE.

19:15.425 --> 19:16.586
SO, WHAT DO YOU THINK'S
CAUSING IT?

19:16.586 --> 19:18.288
I DON'T KNOW.
THAT'S A FIRST.

19:18.288 --> 19:19.829
YEAH.
WE SOLVED THE SHOOTING.

19:19.829 --> 19:22.662
NOW IT'S JUST A MEDICAL MYSTERY,
SO YOU CAN GO HOME.

19:23.893 --> 19:25.795
DID I DO SOMETHING
TO OFFEND YOU?

19:25.795 --> 19:28.268
WHAT? NO, WHY?
LET'S SEE.

19:28.268 --> 19:30.370
YOU TURNED DOWN MY CASE,
WHICH YOU'VE NEVER DONE BEFORE.

19:30.370 --> 19:31.841
YOU GET ON A PLANE.
YOU FLY TO PENNSYLVANIA,

19:31.841 --> 19:34.704
WHEN I CAN BARELY GET YOU
TO RIDE THE ELEVATOR.

19:34.704 --> 19:37.747
YOU'RE SHOT AT,
BUT YOU DON'T WANT MY HELP.

19:37.747 --> 19:39.309
AND NOW I'M HERE,

19:39.309 --> 19:40.880
AND YOU CAN'T RUSH ME
OUT OF TOWN FAST ENOUGH.

19:40.880 --> 19:42.552
NOW, WHAT THE HELL
IS GOING ON?!
IT'S -- IT'S NOTHING.

19:42.552 --> 19:43.913
Natalie: DANIEL,

19:43.913 --> 19:46.486
THIS WOMAN CRACKS
SERIAL KILLERS FOR A LIVING.

19:46.486 --> 19:47.717
ONE WAY OR ANOTHER,

19:47.717 --> 19:49.519
SHE'S GONNA GET
THE TRUTH OUT OF YOU.

19:49.519 --> 19:51.221
KATE, I...
[ SIGHS ]

19:51.221 --> 19:53.723
I CAN'T HAVE A RELATIONSHIP
WITH YOU.

19:53.723 --> 19:56.626
OKAY, WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

19:56.626 --> 19:59.229
OH, WE PROBABLY SHOULD HAVE
ROLE-PLAYED THIS FIRST.

19:59.229 --> 20:01.231
I -- I MEAN, I CAN'T --

20:01.231 --> 20:03.873
I CAN'T HAVE A-A RELATIONSHIP
WITH ANYBODY RIGHT NOW.

20:03.873 --> 20:05.875
OKAY, WHAT GAVE YOU
THE IMPRESSION

20:05.875 --> 20:07.807
THAT I WANTED
A RELATIONSHIP?

20:07.807 --> 20:11.411
I DON'T KNOW.
UH, I GUESS...

20:11.411 --> 20:13.983
UH, MAYBE I WAS --
I WAS PICKING UP SIGNALS.

20:13.983 --> 20:17.417
IF I HAD FEELINGS FOR YOU,
I WOULD LET YOU KNOW,

20:17.417 --> 20:20.620
PROBABLY IN SOME UNBELIEVABLY
IRRESISTIBLE WAY.

20:20.620 --> 20:22.492
I WOULDN'T BE SENDING OUT
SIGNALS, OKAY?

20:22.492 --> 20:24.724
[ CHUCKLES ]
I'M JUST SAYING --

20:24.724 --> 20:27.797
I AM NOT SOME DOTING STUDENT
WITH A SCHOOLGIRL CRUSH.

20:27.797 --> 20:30.800
NOW, DANIEL, LIKE A LOT OF
OTHER THINGS WITH YOU,

20:30.800 --> 20:33.333
THIS IS
ALL IN YOUR HEAD.

20:33.333 --> 20:37.267
OH, AND DON'T WORRY
ABOUT AVOIDING ME ANYMORE.

20:37.267 --> 20:39.309
I'M GONNA LEAVE TONIGHT.

20:39.309 --> 20:42.872
KATE, I-I --

20:45.315 --> 20:48.318
"TELL HER THE TRUTH."
THAT WAS A GREAT IDEA.

20:48.318 --> 20:52.021
THE IDEA WASN'T BAD.
THE EXECUTION WAS A LITTLE OFF.

20:52.021 --> 20:53.623
THIS WHOLE TRIP
HAS BEEN A DISASTER.

20:53.623 --> 20:56.626
HERE I AM,
STUCK IN THIS GODFORSAKEN TOWN

20:56.626 --> 20:57.987
IN THAT NIGHTMARE
OF A HOTEL

20:57.987 --> 20:59.589
WHERE ALL THE FURNITURE'S
IN THE WRONG PLACE.

20:59.589 --> 21:01.331
YOU'RE NOT UPSET
ABOUT THE FURNITURE.

21:01.331 --> 21:02.592
YOU'RE UPSET ABOUT KATE.

21:02.592 --> 21:04.534
YES, OF COURSE
I'M UPSET ABOUT KATE.

21:04.534 --> 21:06.366
HER FRIENDSHIP
IS IMPORTANT TO ME,

21:06.366 --> 21:08.768
AND I PROBABLY
JUST RUINED THAT.

21:08.768 --> 21:11.741
ARE YOU SURE
THAT'S WHAT'S BOTHERING YOU?

21:11.741 --> 21:13.643
EVEN IF YOU DON'T WANT
A RELATIONSHIP,

21:13.643 --> 21:16.005
IT'S ALWAYS NICE TO THINK
SOMEONE HAS A CRUSH ON YOU.

21:16.005 --> 21:17.877
[ SIGHS ]
YOU KNOW WHAT, I'M FINE.

21:17.877 --> 21:19.609
I'M FINE.
[ STAMMERS ]

21:19.609 --> 21:21.481
THIS CONVERSATION IS OVER.
I HAVE WORK TO DO.

21:21.481 --> 21:24.013
BURYING YOUR EMOTIONS
ISN'T HEALTHY, DANIEL.

21:24.013 --> 21:26.716
EVENTUALLY THEY BUBBLE
TO THE SURFACE!

21:30.490 --> 21:32.522
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

21:32.522 --> 21:36.295
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

21:36.295 --> 21:37.497
[ RINGING STOPS ]

21:39.829 --> 21:41.571
BAD DAY?

21:41.571 --> 21:44.874
[ CHUCKLES ]
YOU HAVE NO IDEA.

21:46.376 --> 21:47.377
BEER?

21:47.377 --> 21:48.838
WHY NOT?

21:48.838 --> 21:51.511
WE'RE ON A ROAD TRIP.
LET'S GET A LITTLE CRAZY.

21:52.542 --> 21:53.743
BUT JUST ONE, THOUGH.

21:55.815 --> 21:57.687
AHH.

21:57.687 --> 22:01.751
YOU KNOW,
WE DON'T TALK ENOUGH.

22:01.751 --> 22:05.024
WE SHOULD TALK DAILY --
HOURLY.

22:05.024 --> 22:08.898
THE FRIENDS OF DR. DANIEL PIERCE
SUPPORT CIRCLE.

22:08.898 --> 22:11.030
MM-HMM. EXACTLY.

22:11.030 --> 22:12.602
AND THE FIRST RULE

22:12.602 --> 22:15.735
OF THE DR. DANIEL
FRIENDS SUPPORT CIRCLE IS...

22:15.735 --> 22:17.336
DON'T TALK ABOUT --

22:17.336 --> 22:20.440
BE IMPERVIOUS TO ALL INSULTS
AND OFFENSIVE COMMENTS.

22:20.440 --> 22:22.912
AH.
[ LAUGHS ]

22:25.074 --> 22:29.419
HEY, MAX, DO YOU, UH...
DO YOU THINK I GIVE SIGNALS?

22:29.419 --> 22:30.520
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

22:30.520 --> 22:33.122
LIKE, DO I SEEM FLIRTY
TO YOU?

22:33.122 --> 22:36.686
ARE YOU TRYING TO BE FLIRTY
WITH ME?

22:36.686 --> 22:39.689
BECAUSE YOU
ARE REALLY FINE --

22:39.689 --> 22:40.930
LIKE "MAXIM" FINE.

22:40.930 --> 22:43.062
OKAY, NO, NOT --

22:43.062 --> 22:47.066
NOT FLIRTY WITH YOU,
UH, PER -- PER SAY.

22:47.066 --> 22:50.470
OH. ARE WE TALKING
ABOUT DR. PIERCE?

22:50.470 --> 22:53.142
HAVE I EVER GIVEN YOU
THE IMPRESSION

22:53.142 --> 22:55.605
THAT I HAVE A THING
FOR HIM?

22:55.605 --> 22:57.106
WELL, DO YOU?
NO.

22:57.106 --> 22:59.749
I JUST WANT TO KNOW
IF I SEEM LIKE I DO.

23:01.411 --> 23:05.154
THIS IS STUPID.
FORGET I...I SAID ANYTHING.

23:05.154 --> 23:07.386
HMM.
ANOTHER BEER?

23:07.386 --> 23:10.560
WE SHOULD TOTALLY
DO THIS AGAIN.

23:10.560 --> 23:12.422
[ BURPS ] OOH.

23:12.422 --> 23:14.824
OKAY, WOW.

23:14.824 --> 23:17.697
[ MAHLER'S "SYMPHONY NO. 5"
PLAYS ]

23:17.697 --> 23:19.699
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLES,
MUSIC STOPS ]

23:24.033 --> 23:27.006
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLING,
LIGHTS POPPING ]

23:27.006 --> 23:30.740
PATTI: Help me, please.

