28:49.759 --> 28:53.232
I REMEMBER EVERYBODY
WATCHING MY EVERY MOVE --

28:53.232 --> 28:57.006
WHAT I ATE, WHAT I WORE,
WHO I HUNG OUT WITH.

28:57.006 --> 28:58.768
