29:33.302 --> 29:36.505
ONE OF THE LOSERS,
AND YOU'RE SCARED.

29:36.505 --> 29:39.048
YEAH.

29:39.048 --> 29:43.552
DON'T YOU JUST
WANT TO BE NORMAL AGAIN?

29:43.552 --> 29:47.356
I MEAN,
TO LOOK PRETTY,

29:47.356 --> 29:50.960
