BECAUSE YOU'RE --

29:53.462 --> 29:55.925
BECAUSE I'M SOME TICKING,
STUTTERING FREAK,

29:55.925 --> 29:58.467
AND I JUST WANT IT
TO STOP!

29:58.467 --> 30:00.499
YOU HAVE A SECRET.

30:00.499 --> 30:04.033
AND DR. PIERCE THINKS
THAT HOLDING IT IN

30:04.033 --> 30:07.006
IS WHAT'S CAUSING
THESE SYMPTOMS.

30:08.838 --> 30:11.340
