MRS. SULLIVAN.

36:11.640 --> 36:13.702
HOW DID YOU FIND OUT?

36:13.702 --> 36:15.744
THAT LITTLE TRAMP,
PATTI, TOLD ME.

36:15.744 --> 36:16.905
WHEN DID YOU TALK TO HER?

36:16.905 --> 36:18.477
WHEN I FOUND OUT
WHAT WAS GOING ON

36:18.477 --> 36:21.410
BETWEEN HER AND BRADEN,
I WENT OVER THERE.

36:22.851 --> 36:25.314
IS THAT
WHEN YOU KILLED HER?

36:32.821 --> 36:35.324
OH, GOD. LEAH?

36:35.324 --> 36:37.866
IT WAS AN ACCIDENT.

36:37.866 --> 36:41.330
TELL US WHAT HAPPENED.
MAYBE WE CAN HELP YOU.

36:43.372 --> 36:48.237
THAT MORNING,
BRADEN WAS REALLY UPSET.

36:48.237 --> 36:49.778
BRADEN, TALK TO ME.

36:49.778 --> 36:51.640
LEAVE ME ALONE.

36:51.640 --> 36:53.542
I WAS WORRIED.

36:53.542 --> 36:56.985
WE'D INSTALLED SPYWARE
ON HIS PHONE, SO I CHECKED IT.

36:56.985 --> 37:02.821
I NEVER EXPECTED TO SEE
THAT...VIDEO.

37:05.554 --> 37:07.596
SO I WENT OVER THERE
TO TELL THAT TRAMP

37:07.596 --> 37:09.598
TO KEEP HER DAUGHTER
AWAY FROM MY BOY.

37:09.598 --> 37:11.600
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

37:11.600 --> 37:13.862
BUT IT WAS PATTI
WHO OPENED THE DOOR.

37:13.862 --> 37:16.705
SHE TOLD ME HER MOTHER
WAS IN PITTSBURGH.

37:16.705 --> 37:20.439
AND I REALIZED
WHAT THAT MEANT.

37:20.439 --> 37:22.841
YOU ARE STILL SEEING
EACH OTHER.

37:22.841 --> 37:26.745
[ Voice breaking ]
I WAS SUCH A FOOL.

37:26.745 --> 37:28.417
I SNAPPED.

37:28.417 --> 37:30.819
I TOLD PATTI
TO STAY AWAY FROM BRADEN,

37:30.819 --> 37:33.282
THAT THEY COULDN'T
BE TOGETHER.

37:33.282 --> 37:36.485
BUT SHE DIDN'T CARE.
SHE SAID THEY WERE IN LOVE.

37:36.485 --> 37:37.986
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.

37:37.986 --> 37:39.458
BRADEN HATES YOU!

37:39.458 --> 37:40.859
HE -- HE THINKS
THAT YOU'RE SAD

37:40.859 --> 37:43.892
AND OVERPROTECTIVE
AND DEPRESSING.

37:43.892 --> 37:46.295
AND BRADEN AND I
ARE GONNA BE TOGETHER!

37:46.295 --> 37:48.797
THERE'S NOTHING
THAT YOU CAN DO TO STOP US!

37:48.797 --> 37:51.470
PATTI.

37:51.470 --> 37:52.641
SO, YOU TOLD HER
THE TRUTH?

37:52.641 --> 37:54.373
I HAD TO.

37:54.373 --> 37:56.305
I'M GONNA TELL BRADEN
THE DISGUSTING THINGS YOU SAID

37:56.305 --> 37:57.706
JUST TO KEEP US APART.

37:57.706 --> 37:59.808
I DIDN'T WANT BRADEN TO KNOW
WHAT HE'D DONE.

38:01.009 --> 38:03.612
I DIDN'T THINK
HE COULD BEAR THE SHAME.

38:03.612 --> 38:06.054
I COULDN'T LET HER TELL HIM.

38:06.054 --> 38:11.560
I ONLY WANTED TO CALM HER DOWN,
TALK SOME SENSE INTO HER.

38:11.560 --> 38:12.961
BUT SHE WOULDN'T LET ME.

38:24.933 --> 38:28.737
PATTI!

38:28.737 --> 38:30.439
I BARELY TOUCHED HER.

38:30.439 --> 38:31.810
SHE PROBABLY HAD
A HEART ATTACK.

38:31.810 --> 38:34.643
IT HAPPENS TO KIDS
WITH NEUROFIBROMATOSIS.

38:34.643 --> 38:35.984
A HEART ATTACK?

38:35.984 --> 38:38.687
YOU SEE, I TOLD YOU
IT WASN'T MY FAULT.

38:38.687 --> 38:40.889
WELL, IT'S MANSLAUGHTER
AT LEAST,

38:40.889 --> 38:42.651
AND YOU STAGED
THE SUICIDE,

38:42.651 --> 38:44.353
ALL TO KEEP YOURSELF
OUT OF JAIL.

38:44.353 --> 38:46.395
NO.

38:46.395 --> 38:48.597
TO KEEP MY SON
FROM LEARNING THE TRUTH.

38:48.597 --> 38:52.661
HOW COULD YOU?

38:52.661 --> 38:54.863
THIS IS ALL YOUR FAULT,
MARTIN.

38:54.863 --> 38:57.035
IF YOU HADN'T CHEATED ON ME

38:57.035 --> 38:59.638
AND LIED TO ME
ALL THESE YEARS,

38:59.638 --> 39:02.070
NONE OF THIS
WOULD HAVE EVER HAPPENED.

39:07.546 --> 39:09.478
Natalie: GLAD TO BE BACK,

39:09.478 --> 39:11.119
WHERE EVERYTHING'S
IN ITS RIGHT PLACE?

39:13.482 --> 39:15.654
ACTUALLY,
YOU KNOW WHAT?

39:15.654 --> 39:22.491
I KIND OF GOT USED TO THE DESK
FACING THE WINDOW IN THE HOTEL.

39:22.491 --> 39:23.732
WE SHOULD TRY MOVING IT.

39:23.732 --> 39:24.993
REALLY?
YOU SURE ABOUT THAT?

39:24.993 --> 39:27.035
YEAH,
I-I CAN BE FLEXIBLE.

39:28.497 --> 39:31.139
LET'S -- LET'S TRY IT.
COME ON. LET'S MOVE IT.

39:38.677 --> 39:41.480
I COULD
GET USED TO THIS.

39:41.480 --> 39:44.152
YEAH?

39:44.152 --> 39:47.916
NO. NO, NO.
NOPE. NO. BACK. BACK.

39:49.618 --> 39:53.091
HERE'S YOUR PONZI-SCHEME
RESEARCH.

39:53.091 --> 39:56.625
WHAT THE HELL WERE YOU DOING
RUNNING OFF TO PENNSYLVANIA

39:56.625 --> 39:58.427
WHEN YOU HAD A CASE WITH ME?

39:58.427 --> 39:59.468
DANIEL NEEDED MY HELP.

39:59.468 --> 40:01.430
I'LL BET HE DID.

40:01.430 --> 40:03.702
WHAT'S THAT
SUPPOSED TO MEAN?

40:03.702 --> 40:05.434
I UNDERSTAND
THAT YOU ADMIRE THE GUY.

40:05.434 --> 40:08.477
HE'S BRILLIANT.
HE'S ALSO COMPLETELY UNSTABLE.

40:08.477 --> 40:10.439
YOU'RE NEVER
GOING TO BE ABLE TO HAVE

40:10.439 --> 40:12.010
A HEALTHY RELATIONSHIP
WITH SOMEBODY LIKE THAT.

40:12.010 --> 40:15.113
YOU SAID SOMETHING TO HIM,
DIDN'T YOU?

40:15.113 --> 40:16.785
WHAT? NO.
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

40:16.785 --> 40:19.748
OKAY, DONNIE,
I CAN TELL WHEN YOU'RE LYING.

40:19.748 --> 40:22.651
YOUR FACE LOOKS LIKE...
THAT.

40:22.651 --> 40:25.454
OKAY. FINE.

40:25.454 --> 40:28.997
MAYBE I HAD A LITTLE
MAN-TO-MAN WITH HIM.

40:28.997 --> 40:30.759
YOU ARE UNBELIEVABLE,
YOU KNOW THAT?!

40:30.759 --> 40:32.631
WHAT IS THIS,

40:32.631 --> 40:34.733
LIKE YOUR JUVENILE WAY
OF TRYING TO GET ME BACK?
NO.

40:34.733 --> 40:36.835
I KNOW I LOST MY CHANCE
WITH YOU A LONG TIME AGO.

40:36.835 --> 40:38.807
I REALIZE THAT.
I JUST...

40:38.807 --> 40:40.739
I JUST WANT YOU
TO BE HAPPY.

40:40.739 --> 40:42.741
OKAY, WELL, FORGIVE ME
IF I FIND THAT

40:42.741 --> 40:44.072
A LITTLE HARD TO SWALLOW.

40:44.072 --> 40:48.176
IN FUTURE, STAY THE HELL
OUT OF MY PERSONAL LIFE.

40:48.176 --> 40:50.779
[ SIGHS ]

40:50.779 --> 40:55.684
FREUD ONCE SAID,
"NO MORTAL CAN KEEP A SECRET.

40:55.684 --> 40:59.187
"IF HIS LIPS ARE SILENT,
HE CHATTERS WITH HIS FINGERTIPS.

40:59.187 --> 41:03.061
BETRAYAL OOZES
OUT OF EVERY PORE."

41:03.061 --> 41:06.595
I THINK OLD SIGMUND
MIGHT HAVE BEEN ONTO SOMETHING.

41:06.595 --> 41:11.239
ALTHOUGH WE MAY BE DESPERATE
TO KEEP OUR SECRETS,

41:11.239 --> 41:13.542
THE HARDER
WE TRY TO BURY THEM,

41:13.542 --> 41:15.774
THE MORE
THEY RISE TO THE SURFACE.

41:15.774 --> 41:20.809
WE ARE NEUROLOGICALLY
COMPELLED TO CONFESS.

41:23.952 --> 41:26.655
AND THAT'S A GOOD THING.

41:26.655 --> 41:29.658
'CAUSE CONFESSION
IS GOOD FOR THE BODY.

41:29.658 --> 41:32.190
IT'S GOOD FOR THE BRAIN.

41:32.190 --> 41:34.192
MIGHT EVEN BE GOOD
FOR THE SOUL,

41:34.192 --> 41:36.194
IF YOU BELIEVE
IN THAT SORT OF THING.
